text: Markus Wechsler (born 9 November 1960) is a Swiss rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Switzerland Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
